Name: ProcessingEventSchemeName
Description: A name for the ProcessingEventScheme. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the ProcessingEventScheme. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the ProcessingEventScheme. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: ProcessingEventSchemeReference
Description: Reference to an existing ProcessingEventScheme for inclusion.

Name: ProcessingEventReference
Description: A ProcessingEvent described in the ProcessingEventScheme.

Name: ProcessingEventGroupReference
Description: A description of a group of ProcessingEvent for administrative or conceptual purposes.
